query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS computational_thinking_scores (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  studentId INT NOT NULL,
  dimension ENUM('decomposition', 'pattern_recognition', 'abstraction', 'algorithms') NOT NULL,
  score INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  exercisesCompleted INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  lastUpdated TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  UNIQUE KEY uniqueStudentDimension (studentId, dimension)
)
